e building. There are many types of ghosts, and the method of exorcism is different. Before you completely determine the type and characteristics of the ghost, do not act rashly, it will harm you! You need to use dozens of spiritually exploring tools to investigate the ghost in the house to determine the type and characteristics of the ghost. You must go through the tutorial to grasp some basic skill. \nNow we offer you $1500 as a initial funding, a two hours online time for free,and unlock the whole 3 maps for early access at very first time! Just rush to find some Exorcists,and enjoy the breath-taking trip and a creepy summer time!\nFor better game experience, just join our Community-Discord\uff1a https://discord.gg/XTQSvRyuNs", "short_description": "\"Exorcism Agency Demo\" is a new packaged version base on Exorcism Agency official version v106. Now you have chance to experiencing multiplayer func with all exorcism tools and 3 maps. Taste the creepy moment and team up with your friends to exorcism it! "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.atombits.cn/privacy-policy-3", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "AtomBits Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.atombits.cn/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "es", "ru", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "CO_OP", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "26766